reviewText: It was not what I wanted, very deceptive advertising.
This one is Not the Movie, don't be fooled like I was, its a crashing into things video, car wrecks, etc.

This movie is silly fun.  From the hell cop to Hoffa's bar and grill, there is a lot to laugh at.  Although the acting isn't fantastic, I thought the story was fairly clever too.  One of my favorites...
